{
  "stem": "12684.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They all had to go through Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you always had to wait until no cars were coming, and some black policeman was standing there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And now you can go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Isn't that really odd, eerie?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You had to work in different things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There was called something [NON-ENGLISH], which means you had to do for 100 hours the dirtiest work they give you to be then entitled to get a little better jobs, or some occupation which is not so tearing on your nerves, or which is not so dirty.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But all the newcomers had to do the dirtiest work, of course.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had to take care of people who came with transports.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And those which were dead and couldn't leave the trains, we had to cart out and close their eyes, which is not very pleasant.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And take care of people in an insane asylum, or in a hospital, people are really very sick.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or I mean, things which are really very bad for you, which somehow had nothing to do with the work you did but with the things you saw-- everlasting impressions, which are very bad.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "100 Hours, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't do them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because my grandfather saw me and took me aside and said that this is not the thing for me to do.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, well, these are the rules.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I cannot bend them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I cannot make new-- I cannot bend them, I cannot make new ones.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he declared that rules can be bent, and ideas can be-- you can have another idea.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Think about it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was very good in that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so another girl and I started to think about that.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
